{"tid":1406052,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新盾 新武器 成本：100都唔洗","createTime":"2019-08-04T12:02:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T14:44:54.000Z","uid":216002,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"65a6cd96ec278995ee3af7145df2f41675b0d078","tid":1406052,"uid":216002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T12:02:42.000Z","msg":"岩先係屋企做瑜珈，心血來潮同家姐整左個盾，都有啲厚度，但唔知大家點睇。<br />\n包住個紙皮先 （紙皮放係中間）長大約40cm左右<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wu5f8ts.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwu5f8ts.png&h=c005b1dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n然後將個墊對摺<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NChFz8Z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNChFz8Z.png&h=0281b21d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n然後再對摺<br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/dkX2Ouo.png[/img］\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdkX2Ouo.png%5B%2Fimg%EF%BC%BD&d=8tXbBdGphLRwD8DFuLHjuAEDdXZq%2B7ycbDpBQOFx8Mg%3D&h=095151b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/dkX2Ouo.png[/img］</a><br />\n完成圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uYD9tuv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuYD9tuv.png&h=871b9e0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔知成效大唔大 但如果唔work 用黎包盾又得唔得？夠厚又夠輕 可以作一個緩衝力<br />\n<br />\n另外，曾經好hit一個香口膠實驗，係講香口膠<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">好有衝擊力</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/9GOhXA7CYwU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F9GOhXA7CYwU&d=8tXbBdGphLRwD8DFuLHjuAEDdXZq%2B7ycbDpBQOFx8Mg%3D&h=9f6abaae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/9GOhXA7CYwU</a><br />\n<br />\n細細舊，就可以整爛西瓜、椰子。而呢啲野係要用刀先開到。如果用黎停車、擋人又得唔得呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdee85e0c45fd174004faa0c42a7d90ca7c0382e","tid":1406052,"uid":216002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T12:03:10.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"c1db0dfaa00a52af542d0660